---
title: Graveyard Beef and Onion Pie with Cheesy Mashed Potato Top and Green Beans
description: This Graveyard Beef and Onion Pie with Cheesy Mashed Potato Top and Green Beans is a frightfully delicious family feast. A dish just right for Halloween or chilly autumn evenings.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220815_R10_W40_UK_F12308-2_MB_Main_low-660ef13b.jpg
